    <td colspan="1" valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="5" color="black">
    Minor Illusion</font></td>
    <td colspan="2" valign="top" align="left"><font color="black"><img
    src="http://205.229.72.28/ev1/public_html/images/magic.gif" width="216" height="30" align="right"></font></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan = "3">
    <!--<a href="magic.asp?mode=updateform&amp;ID=113">-->
    <a href="../UserUpdate.asp?ID=113">
    <small><font color="#000080" face="Verdana"><strong>Add New Info Here</strong></font></small>
    </a>
    </td>
    
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
    <b>Description:</b> <br>
    Changes form of the caster only to that of nearby object. Can take on varied, random and numerous forms depending of the surroundings. Its pretty interesting to see a chair that talks.<BR>
<BR>
<B>Location:</B><BR>General<br>
    <b>Effects:</b><br>
    Will Become the nearest non-living object.
    </font>
    
    </td>
    <td rowspan="2" valign="top" align="right"><font
    face="verdana" color="black" size="1">
    
