				Just wanted to add my little story...<BR>
  I was on Orc Hill in Greater Faydark.  I dropped a sword on the ground and cast Minor Illusion.  I picked up the sword, and started fighting orcs.  I got some comments from people around, and had fun scaring others...the talking sword strikes again...hahaha.  When the spell started to fade I cast MI, but becuase I had picked up the sword already and there was nothing else around, the illusion failed...or did it.  I suddenly found that I could move around...as the sword.  Boy was this fun...I asked around and they said I looked like a sword and the orcs ignored me...just like when the spell was on.  This maybe a glitch or bug, but it was fun, and I don't want to ruin that.<BR>
